    <section class="instructions-section">
    
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Guidelines</h2>
            <p>If you consistently consume fewer calories than you burn, your weight will decrease over time.</p>
            <p>Average Daily Calorie Deficit = (calories burned per day)  - (calories consumed per day) </p>
            <p>A 500 calorie/day average deficit results in a 1 lb/week weight loss.</p>
            <p>A 1000 calorie/day average deficit results in a 2 lb/week weight loss.</p>
        </div>
    
    </section>
    <section class="instructions .card-grid">
        <div class="setup-form card">
            <h2>Initial Set-Up for Your 5 Week Plan</h2>
            <p>Today is day 0.  What do you weigh today?</p>
            <form>
                <div class="form-control showcase-form">
                    <input id="user-name" type="text" name="dbusername" placeholder="Enter Your Name" required>
                </div>

                <div class="form-control showcase-form">
                    <input id="start-weight" type="text" name="starting-weight" placeholder="Enter Starting Weight" required>
                </div>
            <p>What is your average daily calorie deficit goal for the next 5 weeks? </p>    
                <div class="form-control showcase-form">
                        <input id="deficit-goal" type="text" name="daily-deficit-goal" placeholder="Enter Daily Calorie Deficit" required>
                </div>
                <button id="see-results" class="btn" type="button" name="button">Click to see results</button>
            </form>
        </div>    


       <div class="card2">
            <h1>Your starting weight is <span id="startWeightOut">_______ </span> .</h1>
            <h1>If you average <span id="calDefOut">_______</span> calorie/day deficit,</h1>
            <h1> in 5 weeks you will weigh <span id="goal-weight-output">_______</span> pounds.</h1>
            
            <form action="/" method="POST"> 
                <input  id="user-name" type="text" name="dbusername2"  value = jimmy placeholder="Enter Your Name" required>
                <button class="row4 button-effect btn" type="submit" id="updateDay0">Click to Commit to This Plan</button> 
            </form> 
        </div>
    </section>
 


